{"tid":1473551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［良心歌手］關淑怡生日斥警殺害市民","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T09:42:20.000Z","uid":227673,"like":280,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5501d463fd06276de3c74c62cca3faf7fba93546","tid":1473551,"uid":227673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"關淑怡今天53歲生日，她昨日在Ig有感而發，貼出生日卡，感謝所有粉絲及友人的祝福，稱這個月是她的生日月份，也是糟糕的月份。關淑怡親切地感謝每一位香港市民，同時譴責警方未有保護好市民，以英文斥稱警方：「你是在殺害他們！」她認為法律不外乎人情。<br />\n<br />\n關淑怡又批評「官商勾結製造混亂」，她續說：「使唔使畀屎餵！警察係要保護市民㗎！你哋好自為之，我希望𠵱家警察記得佢小時候，爸爸媽媽點教佢大人係要保護小朋友嘅，暴動嗰個係林鄭同埋何君堯。」她再以英文寫道：「法律規則不是由我們制定的&hellip;&hellip;它是自然法則，各位大德！」一向不平則鳴的關淑怡，早前因不滿黃耀明遭封殺，曾與內地網民爆發罵戰，她更批評部份微博用戶是「沒人權又沒普及教育的一群」。<br />\n撰文︰祖李<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190815&amp;sec_id=462&amp;s=0&amp;a=20749134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190815%26sec_id%3D462%26s%3D0%26a%3D20749134&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=4fb5ed3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190815%26sec_id%3D462%26s%3D0%26a%3D20749134&h=882e8418\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190815&amp;sec_id=462&amp;s=0&amp;a=20749134</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲先係香港藝人應該表嘅態"},{"pid":"9c7adbf12c766017e5352860f590bca7d803e3f1","tid":1473551,"uid":227673,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"今日即刻去買佢新碟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cce44b88ebaf18034bb3dee18df754c438fb5cb","tid":1473551,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b8a5bc5ecc0037b2ccc37ffb2140a05829600e9","tid":1